race.description: Solomon Motor Group Super Maiden Handicap
race.comment: FIREPOP (10) at her top for this fourth-up and will find this more to her liking. Launched late from back in the field with an eye catching fourth over 1100m at Warwick Farm. Can race closer today and shed her Maiden status. SAYONARA TWO STEP (13) even debut when she failed to close off to run seventh at Gosford over 1000m. This looks much easier and the inside gate helps her cause. SIR WILLIAM (8) gripped on late in the heavy (10) going with a handy third over 1280m at Orange. Minor contender. COSMONAUT (6) drops back to country level today and should be at his peak now at his fourth run back this time in. May find this a touch easier and can improve.
